---
---

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-['Outfit'] text-[#0f3e68] mb-4">
        Fitur Unggulan BAHARI
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg">
        Solusi lengkap untuk koperasi desa dan masyarakat pesisir
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6">
      
      {/* Card 1 */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-slate-100 flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-[#0f3e68]">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 2 3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4Z"/><path d="M3 6h18"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0f3e68] font-['Outfit'] text-xl mb-3">Marketplace</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Akses pasar langsung untuk nelayan dan koperasi. Jual ke restoran, hotel, pasar, hingga rumah tangga.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Card 2 */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-slate-100 flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-[#0f3e68]">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 17h4V5H2v12h3"/><path d="M20 17h2v-9l-5-1H14"/><path d="M14 17h1"/><circle cx="7.5" cy="17.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="17.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0f3e68] font-['Outfit'] text-xl mb-3">Cold Chain Desa</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Fasilitas penyimpanan dingin di tingkat desa untuk menjaga kesegaran dan kualitas hasil tangkapan.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Card 3 */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-slate-100 flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-green-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-green-600">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z"/><path d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0f3e68] font-['Outfit'] text-xl mb-3">Eco Point</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Dapatkan poin dari aksi menjaga lingkungan seperti mengumpulkan sampah laut dan menukarnya dengan berbagai hadiah.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Card 4 */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-slate-100 flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-emerald-600">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12V7H5a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h14v4"/><path d="M3 5v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16v-5"/><path d="M18 12a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h4v-4Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0f3e68] font-['Outfit'] text-xl mb-3">Akses Keuangan</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Riwayat transaksi dan aktivitas digunakan untuk mendapatkan akses pinjaman usaha, BPJS, dan program bantuan lainnya.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Card 5 */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-slate-100 flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-purple-600">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16Z"/><path d="m3.3 7 8.7 5 8.7-5"/><path d="M12 22V12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0f3e68] font-['Outfit'] text-xl mb-3">Ekonomi Sirkular</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Limbah laut dan sampah plastik diolah menjadi produk bernilai jual untuk menambah penghasilan masyarakat.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
